**1. Executive Summary**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **ELECTRON-4 / ORBIT Mission**                                        |
|                                                                       |
| Automatically publish approved video content to TikTok, Instagram,    |
| and LinkedIn                                                          |
|                                                                       |
| with full operator control, 3-mode scheduling (Manual / Semi-Auto /   |
| Full Auto),                                                           |
|                                                                       |
| and real-time Telegram notifications for every launch.                |
|                                                                       |
| Making health, losing weight, losing fat is FUN --- launched into     |
| orbit.                                                                |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

ELECTRON-4, codenamed ORBIT (Outreach, Reporting, Benchmarks & Insights
Tracker), is the fourth and final agent in the QUANTUM AI Content
Factory pipeline. While ELECTRON-3 produces finished video assets, ORBIT
takes those videos and distributes them across social media platforms on
a controlled schedule.

ORBIT completes the content lifecycle: E1 discovers trends, QUANTUM
plans briefs, E2 writes content, E3 produces videos, and E4 publishes
them to the world. With ORBIT, CorpFit achieves a fully autonomous
content pipeline from trend discovery to social media post.

**1.1 Current Pipeline Status**

  ---------------- --------------- --------------------- -----------------
  **Agent**        **Status**      **Output**            **Feeds Into**

  **ELECTRON-1**   ✅ Production   Trend Board (7-15     QUANTUM
                                   trends)               

  **QUANTUM**      ✅ Production   Content Briefs +      ELECTRON-2
                                   Approval              

  **ELECTRON-2**   ✅ Production   Scripts, Captions, QA ELECTRON-3

  **ELECTRON-3**   ✅ Production   Videos, Thumbnails    ELECTRON-4

  **ELECTRON-4**   **🚀 Planning** Published Posts +     Dashboard / App
                                   Analytics             
  ---------------- --------------- --------------------- -----------------

**1.2 Value Proposition**

-   **Zero-touch publishing:** Videos go from production to live posts
    without manual uploading to each platform.

-   **Mission Control:** Three scheduling modes (Manual, Semi-Auto, Full
    Auto) give operators complete control over what goes live.

-   **Multi-platform:** Single video asset automatically formatted and
    posted to TikTok, Instagram Reels, and LinkedIn.

-   **Audit trail:** Every publish action logged with timestamps,
    platform post IDs, and status tracking.

-   **Client-ready:** Adds massive value to CorpFit\'s service offering
    --- clients get content created AND published.

**2. System Architecture**

**2.1 High-Level Flow**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **ORBIT Pipeline Flow**                                               |
|                                                                       |
| E3 produces video → publish_logs.status = \'ready_to_post\'           |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| ORBIT detects new ready video                                         |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| Mode Check: Manual / Semi-Auto / Full Auto                            |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| \[Manual\] Telegram: \"🚀 Ready for Orbit!\" + platform buttons       |
|                                                                       |
| \[Semi-Auto\] Telegram preview + 30-min auto-launch timer             |
|                                                                       |
| \[Full Auto\] Immediate platform routing                              |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| Platform Router → TikTok API / Instagram Graph API / LinkedIn Posts   |
| API                                                                   |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| Post created → schedule_logs entry with post_id + URL                 |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| Telegram confirmation: \"✅ Posted to TikTok: \[link\]\"              |
|                                                                       |
| ↓                                                                     |
|                                                                       |
| Dashboard: Published tab updated with live links                      |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**2.2 Three Scheduling Modes**

  --------------- ------------ ------------------------ -----------------------
  **Mode**        **Icon**     **Behavior**             **Best For**

  **Manual**      🔴           Every post requires      Launch phase. Building
                               Telegram tap. Operator   trust in the system.
                               picks which platform(s). 

  **Semi-Auto**   🟡           Telegram preview sent.   Comfortable phase.
                               If no Hold within 30     Trust with safety net.
                               min, auto-posts to all   
                               platforms.               

  **Full Auto**   🟢           E3 finishes → E4 posts   Mature phase. Full
                               immediately. Telegram    autonomous pipeline.
                               confirmation only.       
  --------------- ------------ ------------------------ -----------------------

The mode is stored in a system_config table and can be changed via
Telegram command (/orbit_mode manual\|semi\|auto) or the Dashboard
settings. Default mode at launch: Manual.

**2.3 Component Architecture**

  ------------------ ---------------------- ------------------------------
  **Component**      **Technology**         **Purpose**

  **E4 Scheduler**   n8n Workflow           Detects ready videos, applies
                                            mode logic, routes to
