  **Platform         n8n Code Node          Formats payload per platform
  Router**                                  API requirements

  **TikTok           TikTok Content Posting Uploads video via
  Publisher**        API                    PULL_FROM_URL or FILE_UPLOAD

  **Instagram        Instagram Graph API    Creates Reel container, polls
  Publisher**        (Meta)                 status, publishes

  **LinkedIn         LinkedIn Posts +       Initializes upload, transfers
  Publisher**        Videos API             video, creates post

  **Telegram         Telegram Bot API       Sends previews, receives
  Controller**                              platform selections, confirms
                                            posts

  **schedule_logs    PostgreSQL             Tracks every publish attempt
  DB**                                      with status, post IDs, URLs

  **Dashboard Tab**  Cloudflare Worker      New \'Orbit\' tab showing
                                            scheduled/posted/failed
                                            content
