**13. Future Phase: Analytics & Insights**

Once ORBIT is publishing content, the natural next step is tracking
performance. This section outlines the analytics system planned for
Phase 3, which will leverage the platform post IDs stored by ORBIT to
pull engagement data.

-   **TikTok Analytics:** Video views, likes, comments, shares, average
    watch time via Query Video API

-   **Instagram Insights:** Reach, plays, likes, saves, shares, comments
    via GET /{media-id}/insights

-   **LinkedIn Analytics:** Views, time watched, engagement rate via
    Video Analytics API (6-month window)

-   **Unified Dashboard:** All platform metrics in one view, identifying
    top performers and optimal posting times

-   **Smart Recycler:** AI identifies top-performing content for
    repurposing and reposting on different platforms

-   **App API:** Feed performance data into CorpFit mobile app for
    client-facing analytics

